Introduction

JooJiRong is a promotional sub-unit of the South Korean girl group Apink, independently established by its members. The sub-unit is composed of Chorong, Eunji, and Namjoo.

They marked their debut with the release of the song “Be My Self” on April 13, 2020. This track is featured on Apink’s ninth mini-album titled “LOOK.”
